            <li>
              Sports (football, badminton, weightlifting, running, hiking, and
              combat sports).
            </li>
            <li>Taking pictures (albeit I'm not really good at it :p)</li>
            <li>
              Reading non-technical books (novels, religions, history, politics,
              financial, just anything other than comics)
            </li>
            <li>Writing (I write poems sometimes by the way)</li>
            <li>If not for my religion, I'd probably do music too</li>
          </ol>
          <p>
